n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td class=&quot;right&quot;&gt;登录帐号：&lt;/td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; id=&quot;txtUserName&quot; name=&quot;txtUserName&quot; /&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/tr&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;tr&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td class=&quot;right&quot;&gt;用户昵称：&lt;/td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; id=&quot;txtNickname&quot; name=&quot;txtNickname&quot; /&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/tr&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;tr&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td class=&quot;right&quot;&gt;密码：&lt;/td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;input type=&quot;password&quot; id=&quot;txtPassword&quot; name=&quot;txtPassword&quot; /&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/td&gt;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &